            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Tertinius Terentius <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>sibi et Rufiae Helpidi <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iugi</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et Tertio <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> CX et Res<lb break="no" n="4"/>pectae <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> LXXXX <expan><abbr>parent</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Tertinia Grata <expan><abbr>fi</abbr><ex>lia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ben</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mer</abbr><ex>entibus</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>scribend</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>curav</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung für einen Gruftdeckel. Nach Kremer ursprünglich zentral am Sockelgeschoss eines Grabbaus angebracht. Material: nach Traxler sogenanntes Ennser Konglomerat. (B): Egger: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
